<diag type = "test" id = "AHRAP70A8204053003">
<testgroup id = "AHRAP70A8204053004">
<title>
Provjera kruga modula zračnog jastuka vozača (uređaj za napuhavanje)
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite modul zračnog jastuka vozača (uređaj za napuhavanje) sa stupa upravljača. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A8206005"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Odspojite konektor “G11”.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Otpustite kratkospojnu šipku u konektoru SDM-a tako da umetnete alat za otpuštanje priložen sa specijalnim alatom (A).
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Provjerite sljedeće točke.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Otpor između terminala “G11-5” i “G11-6”: beskonačan
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L8B097">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09932-76010">
09932-76010
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<testfigure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAW10A820030.swf" width = "90.000mm" height = "60.504mm" ver = "01" gw = "212" gh = "155"/>
</testfigure>
</test1>
<question>
Jesu li u dobrom stanju?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Idite na 2. korak.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Provjerite radi neispravnog ožičenja. Ako je rezultat provjere u redu, zamijenite sklop zavojnice kontakta. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A6206003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AHRAP70A8204053005">
<title>
Provjera kruga zavojnice kontakta (kruga modula zračnog jastuka vozača (uređaj za napuhavanje))
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite sklop zavojnice kontakta. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A6206003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Provjerite sljedeće točke.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Model s kontakt bravom:
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Izmjerite otpor između terminala “S121-1” do “S172-2” i “S121-2” do “S172-1”.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<ptxt>
Model sa sustavom pokretanja pritiskom bez ključa: 
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Izmjerite otpor između terminala “S121 –1” do “S174-2” i “S121-2” do “S174-1”.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L8B098">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09932-76010">
09932-76010
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<testfigure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A820018.swf" width = "90.000mm" height = "70.672mm" ver = "02" gw = "196" gh = "184"/>
</testfigure>
</test1>
<question>
Je li otpor 1 &#937; ili manji?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Idite na 3. korak.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Zamijenite sklop zavojnice kontakta. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A6206003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AHRAP70A8204053006">
<title>
Provjera kruga zavojnice kontakta (krug sirene)
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Provjerite sljedeće točke.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Model s kontakt bravom:
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
